data.text: Rhydon Atzenhoffer and Dennis Wilkins have one of the best shows of the year for you on tap thanks to returning guest Brittany Murphy from One Thing Marketing. In what is Part 2 of a three episode series of 2023 End of Year Specials, Britt breaks down how to take a look and self evaluate where you are with your marketing and where you can start small in 2024 to make a difference for your company. If you do not learn anything from this show, then you were not paying attention. This is one of the best "Free99" marketing talks you will get as a business owner or future business owner in the Trades. So sit back and enjoy a fun and laughter filled marketing discussion that will help you get serious about your business plan moving forward into a rapidly approaching 2024. Cheers #TradeCrew, thanks for listening. We appreciate all of you for listening to our show every week.
